front.title: •Jabba's Influence
front.gametext: Deploy on one of your gangsters or bounty hunters. Once during each of your control phases, if present with an opponent's smuggler or character of ability = 1, may use 3 Force. Opponent must use 5 Force or that character returns to opponent's hand.
front.lore: Jabba makes offers one cannot refuse. Smugglers, thieves and competitors who do not acquiesce have been rumored to wake up with a bantha's head in their bed.
